  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Monitoring and Evaluation of the Climate Private Public Partnership</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall aim of the CP3 project is to increase the role of private sector finance in driving low carbon, climate resilient growth in developing countries. CP3 aims to increase the amount of funding in Private Equity (PE) in the climate friendly space both by directly funding two commercially run PE Funds (who in turn fund sub funds and projects which would therefore be able to conclude their investments) and thus inducing a leveraging effect, i.e. bringing on board other donors and other institutional investors (sovereign wealth funds, pension funds and insurance funds), as well as by making direct investments in the climate area.</narrative>
  </description>
